    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 19-5-171, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO STIPULATE THAT THE COMMISSIONERS OF THE TISHOMINGO COUNTY WATER DISTRICT SHALL BE COMPENSATED FOR THEIR SERVICES AT A RATE UP TO $84.00 PER DAY UNDER CERTAIN CONDITIONS; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
